title: UFYB 75: Massive Thinking
itunes:title: Massive Thinking
description:
If you're confused or frustrated because the steps you're taking aren't working or getting you any closer to your goals, I'm giving you the answer today. Discover where you might be going wrong in your endeavors to get what you want. What I'm sharing today may seem obvious, but you'll be surprised when you slip back and catch yourself relying on actions alone to create your results.

Get full show notes and more information here: https://unfuckyourbrain.com/75
